section.section:
"Association or organization" means:
An athletic club;
A charitable organization;
A civic league or organization;
A community association;
A cooperative housing corporation as that term is defined under § 5-6B-01 of the Corporations and Associations Article;
A council of unit owners of a condominium as that term is defined in § 11-101 of the Real Property Article; or
A homeowners' association.
